Account & Data Deletion

Users of the Maliya app can delete their account and all associated data instantly at any time directly from the app.

How to delete your account:
Open the Maliya app
Go to Settings
Tap Delete Account
Confirm deletion

Once confirmed, the account deletion process is executed immediately and permanently. All associated data will be removed from our systems, including:

User profile information
Invoices and financial records
Client data
Any stored application data
